DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260515T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Chicago:20260515T210000
SUMMARY:Drum\, shake\, make music.
DESCRIPTION:The Chicago Drum Circle Meetup Group\n• What we'll do\nOpen\, lightly facilitated\, family friendly\, community drum circle.\n\n• What to bring\nBring yourself\, a friend\, and a hand drum\, percussion instrument or a found sound.\n\n• Important to know\nThis is a Ridgeville Park District partnership program. Alcohol\, tobacco\, vaping and drugs are strictly prohibited.
